long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
HungerHub Ratings helps you keep track of your dining experiences on HungerHub. Never forget which restaurants you loved or which ones disappointed.

Key Features:
- Rate your orders with a simple 5-star system
- Add personal comments to remember specific details about your orders
- See your past ratings directly on the orders page
- View average ratings for restaurants while browsing
- Track your ordering history with detailed statistics
- Export and import your ratings data

Works seamlessly with the HungerHub interface
Perfect for teams and individuals who order regularly from HungerHub and want to make informed decisions based on their past experiences.
